\def\ltitle{Infinite dimensional symmetry \cr
           of corner transfer matrices \cr}
\def\stitle{Infinite dimensional symmetry of corner transfer matrices}

\def\lauthor{Brian Davies}

\def\laddress{Department of Mathematics, \hfil\break
School of Mathematical Sciences, \hfil\break
Australian National University, \hfil\break
Canberra, ACT 0200, Australia }

\def\SMS{SMS-118-93}
\def\CMA{CMA-MR55-93}

\def\labstract{
We review some of the recent developments in two dimensional
statistical mechanics in which corner transfer matrices
provide the vital link between the physical system and the
representation theory of quantum affine algebras.
This opens many new possibilities, because the eigenstates may
be described using the properties of $q$-vertex operators.}
%
